html:
Happy Sunday, feline fam. We love to have relax on Sun-if you don't get off the counter we swear to god, no tuna for a week- sorry about that. Our cat has decided that she wishes to sleep on the counters and only there today. Normally, she doesn't get up there, but today, she's really pushing our buttons about it. 

Hey, we see you over there. Don't you even think about it.

Normally our cat is a sweet, precious baby angel, but today, she is choosing to test our patience every second of the day, and to calm down, we need a pleasant and silly scroll through some hissterical cat memes to remind us how much we love our cat and why we should keep her even though she's being a bad girl. Don't worry, we still love her, but boy, does she love to-hey, HEY, get away from there-make our lives chaotic sometimes. Anyway, we hope you enjoy these fluffy feline funnies of sweet baby angel-no, no, NO! We said not on the counters!!!!
